        <source srcset="/img/content/2019-04-22-10.webp" type="image/webp" />
        <img class="img-fluid rounded" width="100%" src="/img/content/2019-04-22-10.png" alt="Figura 6. A classifica√ß√£o do comportamento (ROSENBLUETH; WIENER; BIGELOW, 1948, p. 11)" />
        
